race.comment: Looks a great race for WIMOWEH (10) who finished third when resuming from a spell last start over 1400m at Beaudesert. Strips fitter and has the class to take care of this field. On top. FORTUNAS GIRL (6) made some progress last start to finish fifth over 1100m at Gold Coast when lining up for just the second time at big odds. Can only be better for the experience and worth consideration. SET FOR LIFE (3) was well held last start when friendless in betting over 1600m at Sunshine Coast. Can contest for a place here. CROSS OF SCARLET (11) battled last start to finish seventh over 1400m at Beaudesert. Hasn't done much so far, but fitter and well drawn is one for exotics.
